message.body: Thank you for going out with me. I really enjoy discussion that makes me question my own positions. I don't get that enough. Also. Ah. Let's ignore math problem
failures when I've already conceded cycling, which is my stronger point...and I hope you feel better, and don't think it was a waste of your time.
You seem to think entirely too little of yourself. I had an excellent time and am very glad we were finally able to do it :-)
